{"tid":618462,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"2018年萬人票選「女性聲優人氣排行2017」水瀨祈奪冠","createTime":"2018-04-06T00:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T00:09:08.000Z","uid":138409,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"41f55919cbbb292e1ee91c2d8f86dbecb6c0e6b4","tid":618462,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T00:06:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/archives/50769\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F50769&d=Qkcn4anxcNjNLEy4KtNlZTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=17d23461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/archives/50769</a><br />\n<br />\n原文授權轉載自ACGdoge<br />\n<br />\n萬人票選網站「charapedia」今天公佈了2018年的萬人票選聲優人氣排行女性聲優投票結果，此排行從2015年開始已經蟬聯4次人氣榜首第一的花澤香菜，在今年被水瀨祈終結在了四連冠，水瀨祈成為了今年女性聲優人氣排行的第一位<br />\n<br />\n萬人票選「女性聲優人氣排行2017」：第3位早見沙織、第2位水瀨祈，花澤香菜四連冠！<br />\n其實這個排行5年來女性聲優的變動也不是很大，來來去去就是這20多位女聲優，無非就是排位名次高低的問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">自己喜歡的聲優就是心目中人氣第一的聲優，所以也不用太苛責這個排行為什麼XX不在/不服OO只有第X位等諸如此類</span><br />\n水瀨祈近來的配音作品包括《KiraKira☆光之美少女 A La Mode》的芭菲天使，《Re:Creators》的米特奧拉，中間那段總集篇可以說是《Re:Creators》這原創動畫最大的亮點，自我吐槽很犀利<br />\n還有《少女終末旅行》中的小千，與剛剛完結的《比宇宙更遙遠的地方》中的女主角玉木真理等等<br />\n<br />\n調查期間：2018/3/15～4/4<br />\n投票属性分佈：男性：40.1%　女性：59.9%　10代・20代：62.4%　30代以上：37.6%<br />\n<br />\n第 1 名：水瀨祈<br />\n<br />\n第 2 名：澤城美雪<br />\n<br />\n第 3 名：花澤香菜<br />\n<br />\n第 4 名：悠木碧<br />\n<br />\n第 5 名：佐倉綾音<br />\n<br />\n第 6 名：早見沙織<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">第 7 名：茅野愛衣</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 8 名：釘宮理惠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 9 名：高橋李依<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 10 名：小倉唯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 11 名：水樹奈奈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 12 名：竹達彩奈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 13 名：戶松遙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 14 名：東山奈央<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 15 名：雨宮天<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 16 名：坂本真綾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 17 名：日高里菜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 18 名：南條愛乃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 19 名：日笠陽子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第 20 名：種田梨沙"},{"pid":"4fb33cd6284d885df89a0dcd74b2f5c7c59592d8","tid":618462,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T00:32:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"982e7bb530e7d0dddfc05c91810ef1bcd13e2ac4","tid":618462,"uid":30235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T00:53:06.000Z","msg":"想睇男聲優人氣排行多啲"},{"pid":"84874548db465af6b8f13d89a106856e425b7859","tid":618462,"uid":101485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T01:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 水瀨bb"},{"pid":"b653c4225bc9310260931e51b8e6b712ce29475e","tid":618462,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"第5第7第15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863d6b734c2106d868e47fc07417d7dae5c662eb","tid":618462,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b653c4225bc9310260931e51b8e6b712ce29475e","tid":618462,"uid":86762,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:06:05.000Z","msg":"第5第7第15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:07:32.000Z","msg":"愛衣醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd785b9912ec382b42843d2757aa08f7c8e4d240","tid":618462,"uid":129434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:08:08.000Z","msg":"雨宮天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"